722720f.text:
Riverside Drive, north from West 84th Street, and showing apartment structures on the east side of same, facing Riverside Park. Paralleling the latter is the North (Hudson) River with its Jersey Palisades. In the center of this view, at West 89th Street is the Soldiers and Sailors Monument.
January 28, 1938.
George D. Chinn.

714673f-a.text:
334-336 West 84th Street, south side, between Riverside Drive
and West End Avenue.
About 1923.
Brown Brothers.
Gift of E. M. Jenks.
